	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la">Precor tibi tuisque omnibus foelicissimum annum et faustissima quęque et simul mitto literas, quas heri <placeName ref="l167">Geneva</placeName> accepi.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la">Vides <persName ref="p8033">Bezae</persName> literas meo sigillo obsignatas; reclusas enim mihi misit, ut lectas occluderem et ad te mitterem.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la">Venit etiam heri huc syndici <placeName ref="l167">Genevensis</placeName> <persName ref="p2740">Roseti</persName> frater.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la">Is valde dubitat de his, quę <persName ref="p8033">Beza</persName> scribit de suppresso <persName ref="p3753">Andegavensi</persName>, nec hic huic rei adhuc ulla fides habetur.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la">Crede ergo, quantum voles.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la">Ego alias nihil habeo, et adeo festinanter discedit ille, ut nunc [non] possim plura.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" ana="farewell">Vale.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la"><placeName ref="l41">Bernae</placeName> calendis ianuarii 1569.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la"><persName ref="p8018">I[ohannes] Hall[erus</persName>] tuus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse fehlt.]</note>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
